rows.label: qev092802_MSG0010
rows.name: Ah, thanks for coming.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_JNK0020
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev092802_SEL0030
rows.name: Ask, suspiciously, what the problem is.

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0040
rows.name:
Oh, nothing that serious.
We just wanted your opinion on something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_JNK0050
rows.name: Tease

rows.label: qev092802_SEL0060
rows.name: Joke that you had nothing better to do.

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0070
rows.name:
If a BLADE's got free time, it's a good sign.
Means our home's at peace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0080
rows.name: Now, onto the topic at hand...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0090
rows.name:
Remember what I said about Hraesvelg?
How we'd developed a special system?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0100
rows.name:
These days, with the Skell flight module equipped,
being able to fly is the industry standard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0110
rows.name:
But the Hraesvelg model...
It can achieve an advanced form of flight—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0120
rows.name: an enhanced cruise mode.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0130
rows.name: Basically, it can turn into a jet aircraft for flight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0140
rows.name: Well? Cool, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0150
rows.name:
We're almost finished developing the system.
It should be operational in a matter of days.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0160
rows.name: It's just that...the fine-tuning isn't going so well...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0170
rows.name:
So then, we were hoping a fresh pair of eyes might help.
And who better to ask than you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0180
rows.name: Sheer IMPERTINENCE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0190
rows.name:
We were on the cusp of scoring the windfall of a
lifetime, and a teenybopper beat us to it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0200
rows.name:
Now I hear we have the chance to one-up the girl
and instead you seek advice from THIS outsider![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0210
rows.name:
Impertinence! Im-PERTINENCE!
Don't you have any pride as an engineer?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0220
rows.name:
We're just getting a second opinion from an active Skell pilot.
I think there's merit in that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0230
rows.name:
Anyway, you said we were "beaten to it,"
but I don't recall it being a competition.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0240
rows.name: That thinking is the definition of "impertinence!"[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0250
rows.name: Wha—?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0260
rows.name: This whole industry is a race to the top![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0270
rows.name:
Revolutionary technology lives or dies
in the flames of competition![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0280
rows.name:
My God. I thought finally, I was putting someone
capable at the helm, my dear Alicia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0290
rows.name: ...Ah...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0300
rows.name:
If we don't get ahead of the curve and finish this project,
all our efforts will have been for nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0310
rows.name:
You will return to work, and finalize
cruise mode right now. Clear?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0320
rows.name: C-crystal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0330
rows.name:
Boss, Alicia's been cooped up this whole time,
ever since we landed on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0340
rows.name: Couldn't you cut her some sla—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0350
rows.name:
Hmph. Tell me something, test pilot. What makes
you think I give a damn about your opinion?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0360
rows.name: But she's my—![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0370
rows.name: Yes, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0380
rows.name: I'll finish it right away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0390
rows.name: Wha— Alicia?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0400
rows.name: I'll go now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092802_MSG0410
rows.name: Alicia![ST:wait ]
